{"tid":1564591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開]動議成立跳跳虎基金計劃","createTime":"2019-09-12T23:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T01:00:17.000Z","uid":34816,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f5e8f96db8a0eb85e5817f24c3a96f4b5057bcbd","tid":1564591,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T23:50:05.000Z","msg":"[跳跳虎基金計劃]<br />\n<br />\n有鑑於近日跳閘運動愈趨勢激烈，為了使社會達致和諧有愛，我動議成立一個基金去為呢班跳閘者找數！呢個計劃可以代班學生找罰款，亦可以代佢地捐錢！<br />\n<br />\n建議基金可接受18歲或以下人士申請代替其繳交跳閘罰款。此外每當核實一次市民的跳閘行為，建議基金捐獻一定數額至星火同盟(或其他任何幫助港人之機構)以幫助被捕的抗爭人士。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">(明白有私隱問題，此部分需集思廣益點樣實行)</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n此計劃目的是代替港鐵承擔其社會責任，將港鐵損失之部份收入捐款幫助抗爭人士，並以此呼籲港鐵作為香港公共企業，一同承擔其應盡之責任，回饋香港人及整個社會。<br />\n<br />\n在此特地聲明，此基金之目的並非鼓吹跳閘行為，而是在跳閘行為因公民抗命為無可避免發生時，希望能略盡綿力幫助各抗爭人士。<br />\n<br />\nPS：我只係拋磚比個idea出黎，唔係基金成立/管理人啊，更唔係任職任何慈善機構<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bc3779ef2326664e83f6c6de671d625e55eaa67","tid":1564591,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T23:50:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"064d08d3dc261d91d230d0b9a782f13a8421e201","tid":1564591,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T23:51:17.000Z","msg":"歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93a02e93e0c769a7f9fc3dd8c546f5b70c4ff9b","tid":1564591,"uid":220292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T23:52:52.000Z","msg":"星火有無得直接幫班跳完又比錢既人找數 或者佢哋再整個基金？"},{"pid":"b998e225814822005748c4ab4f472e6a37b0e4c2","tid":1564591,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b93a02e93e0c769a7f9fc3dd8c546f5b70c4ff9b","tid":1564591,"uid":220292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T23:52:52.000Z","msg":"星火有無得直接幫班跳完又比錢既人找數 或者佢哋再整個基金？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T23:54:09.000Z","msg":"如果一個基金專門係幫助跳閘個流程會唔會快d 同簡單d，即係你拎張跳閘罰單黎就可以拎500"},{"pid":"33ac87bf7a303af7f2cbb5f1ceb51dbaee281289","tid":1564591,"uid":220292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b998e225814822005748c4ab4f472e6a37b0e4c2","tid":1564591,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b93a02e93e0c769a7f9fc3dd8c546f5b70c4ff9b","tid":1564591,"uid":220292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T23:52:52.000Z","msg":"星火有無得直接幫班跳完又比錢既人找數 或者佢哋再整個基金？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T23:54:09.000Z","msg":"如果一個基金專門係幫助跳閘個流程會唔會快d 同簡單d，即係你拎張跳閘罰單黎就可以拎500"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T23:55:25.000Z","msg":"呢個時勢 可能得攬炒巴開既基金有人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c602cdfa3d977c5f047ba26cfb1e0706b119de","tid":1564591,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33ac87bf7a303af7f2cbb5f1ceb51dbaee281289","tid":1564591,"uid":220292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b998e225814822005748c4ab4f472e6a37b0e4c2","tid":1564591,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b93a02e93e0c769a7f9fc3dd8c546f5b70c4ff9b","tid":1564591,"uid":220292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T23:52:52.000Z","msg":"星火有無得直接幫班跳完又比錢既人找數 或者佢哋再整個基金？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T23:54:09.000Z","msg":"如果一個基金專門係幫助跳閘個流程會唔會快d 同簡單d，即係你拎張跳閘罰單黎就可以拎5